  "character_description": "Martin Urbano is a spell-casting stage comic fighter with shoulder-length dark wavy hair, warm medium skin, a black overshirt over a white graphic T-shirt, dark pants, and white sneakers. He carries a small spiral notepad and pen instead of a microphone; every spell starts as something he writes.\n\nSilhouette: slim upright performer stance, expressive hair, notepad in off hand, pen hand ready to cast.\nClothing: black open overshirt/jacket, white tee with a simple green graphic, dark pants, white sneakers.\nHair: shoulder-length dark wavy hair with a loose side part.\nAccessories: small notepad and pen only; no microphone.\nAttitude: clever spell-slinger, theatrical but precise.\nDistinctive traits: glowing written sigils, firebolt writing spell, oversized golden pen-blade special.",
